EU Says Hungary Telecom Tax Is Illegal in ’Clear-Cut Case’

-- B y   A n d r e w   C l a p h a m
-- 
2011-09-29T10:27:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-29/eu-says-hungary-telecom-tax-is-illegal-in-clear-cut-case-.html
Hungary’s “specific turnover” tax
on telecommunications operators is “illegal” in a “clear-
cut” case, European Commission spokesman  Jonathan Todd  told
reporters today in Brussels.  The commission has told Hungary to end the tax.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
